Package org.group8.simulator.model

Class Distribution

java.lang.Object
org.group8.simulator.model.Distribution
@Entity public class Distribution extends Object
Represents a distribution entity for an event in the simulation. This class is mapped to the "distribution" table in the database. It contains information about the event, its associated distribution, and the average time for the event.
